<Link id="l00197" /><CodeLine lineNumber="197"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The core of the Dwarf linking logic.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00198" /><CodeLine lineNumber="198"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00199" /><CodeLine lineNumber="199"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The generation of the dwarf information from the object files will be</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00200" /><CodeLine lineNumber="200"><Highlight kind="comment">/// driven by the selection of &#39;root DIEs&#39;, which are DIEs that</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00201" /><CodeLine lineNumber="201"><Highlight kind="comment">/// describe variables or functions that resolves to the corresponding</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00202" /><CodeLine lineNumber="202"><Highlight kind="comment">/// code section(and thus have entries in the Addresses map). All the debug</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00203" /><CodeLine lineNumber="203"><Highlight kind="comment">/// information that will be generated(the DIEs, but also the line</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00204" /><CodeLine lineNumber="204"><Highlight kind="comment">/// tables, ranges, ...) is derived from that set of root DIEs.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00205" /><CodeLine lineNumber="205"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00206" /><CodeLine lineNumber="206"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The root DIEs are identified because they contain relocations that</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00207" /><CodeLine lineNumber="207"><Highlight kind="comment">/// points to code section(the low&#95;pc for a function, the location for</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00208" /><CodeLine lineNumber="208"><Highlight kind="comment">/// a variable). These relocations are called ValidRelocs in the</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00209" /><CodeLine lineNumber="209"><Highlight kind="comment">/// AddressesInfo and are gathered as a very first step when we start</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00210" /><CodeLine lineNumber="210"><Highlight kind="comment">/// processing a object file.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00211" /><CodeLine lineNumber="211" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/classic/dwarflinker"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">class </Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/classic/dwarflinker/#a419275b4bdc8a89c7cce1506c7f24345">DWARFLinker</a> : </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">public</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/dwarflinkerbase">DWARFLinkerBase</a> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
